Package: zerotier-gateway-controller
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-requests, python3-yaml, iputils-ping
Description: Automated failover controller for ZeroTier network gateways
 This service monitors gateway health and dynamically updates ZeroTier network routes
 to ensure high availability access to a home subnet. Features include priority-based
 failover, API-based route management, logging, and optional Grafana Cloud integration.
